# Entra Connect Monitoring Module

**Author:** Adrian Johnson (adrian207@gmail.com)  
**Version:** 1.0.0  
**Date:** December 2024

This module provides comprehensive monitoring and performance analysis for Entra Connect.

## Functions

### Get-EntraConnectSyncMetrics
Retrieves synchronization performance metrics.

### Monitor-EntraConnectHealth
Monitors overall health status.

### Get-EntraConnectSyncErrors
Identifies and reports sync errors.

### Set-EntraConnectAlerting
Configures monitoring alerts.

### Get-EntraConnectPerformanceReport
Generates performance analysis reports.

### Monitor-EntraConnectConnectivity
Monitors Azure connectivity.

### Get-EntraConnectAuditLogs
Retrieves audit log information.

### Set-EntraConnectLogging
Configures detailed logging.

### Get-EntraConnectCapacityMetrics
Monitors capacity and resource usage.

### Generate-EntraConnectReport
Creates comprehensive status reports.
